WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
narrator: tour the analytics indexer surface — three endpoints.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
narrator: bring the mesh and analytics indexer up together.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:50.000
narrator: the indexer scans the audit-dir on a fixed cadence.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:30.000
narrator: a Hub-free mesh writes no audit log; counters stay at zero.

00:01:55.000 --> 00:02:05.000
narrator: bringup completes — the analytics surface is live.

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:14.000
narrator: /metrics returns Prometheus text counters for scraping.

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:24.000
narrator: /analytics/health surfaces last-scan and audit-dir state.

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:34.000
narrator: /analytics/series buckets session-open counts per minute.

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:44.000
narrator: the same surface for preauth_minted on a 1-minute bucket.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:54.000
narrator: the node also exposes its own /metrics when Hub-mounted.

00:02:55.000 --> 00:03:04.000
narrator: teardown — observability shape demonstrated end-to-end.
